?m=1644885960", "title": "汽车", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/car", "topics": 1763, "footer": "", "header": "关于买车、开车及汽车文化的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Car", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960", "stars": 1656, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 176, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 91197, "username": "f2ck", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/f2ck", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc3d/0a0a/91197_mini.png?m=1691659707", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc3d/0a0a/91197_normal.png?m=1691659707", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc3d/0a0a/91197_large.png?m=1691659707", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc3d/0a0a/91197_xlarge.png?m=1691659707", "created": 1420967364, "last_modified": 1691659707}, "last_reply_by": "xdzhang", "last_touched": 1698458476, "title": "我想问下不支持不买电车的那波人是在担心什么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/985987", "created": 1698385723, "deleted": 0, "content": "有可能是引战的话题。", "content_rendered": "有可能是引战的话题。", "last_modified": 1698385897, "replies": 139, "id": 985987}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 5015, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1250, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 646446, "username": "smallpampan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/smallpampan", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_mini.png?m=1698292303", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_normal.png?m=1698292303", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_large.png?m=1698292303", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_xlarge.png?m=1698292303", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_xlarge.png?m=1698292303", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7994/42fd/646446_xlarge.png?m=1698292303", "created": 1693485237, "last_modified": 1698292303}, "last_reply_by": "ashin", "last_touched": 1698459009, "title": "如果可以不工作，你想做什么？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/985967", "created": 1698380617, "deleted": 0, "content": "不工作躺平一个多月了，去过旅游、City walk 、泡图书馆复习、看电影、拍 vlog 、写 blog 、溜狗、锻炼健身、海边发呆等等。\r\n退休生活莫过如此？\r\n但是感觉时间久了就有点无趣，特别是早上遛狗时，遇到都是大妈带着孩子遛弯，大爷打太极，过于安逸到都感受到生机萧条。\r\n躺平久了对生活盼头、欲望都降低了。\r\n所以我应该做点什么呢？\r\n很想知道，别人如果不工作，都想去做什么？\r\n又或者有理想的人都想去做什么？\r\n又或者作为一个人都需要有什么理想？", "content_rendered": "<p>不工作躺平一个多月了，去过旅游、City walk 、泡图书馆复习、看电影、拍 vlog 、写 blog 、溜狗、锻炼健身、海边发呆等等。\n退休生活莫过如此？\n但是感觉时间久了就有点无趣，特别是早上遛狗时，遇到都是大妈带着孩子遛弯，大爷打太极，过于安逸到都感受到生机萧条。\n躺平久了对生活盼头、欲望都降低了。\n所以我应该做点什么呢？\n很想知道，别人如果不工作，都想去做什么？\n又或者有理想的人都想去做什么？\n又或者作为一个人都需要有什么理想？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1698382297, "replies": 132, "id": 985967}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_large.png?m=1542423096", "name": "guangzhou", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_normal.png?m=1542423096", "title": "广州", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou", "topics": 1244, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Guangzhou", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096", "stars": 1359, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 20, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 50757, "username": "yyd1000", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yyd1000", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75eb/5900/50757_mini.png?m=1392705722", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75eb/5900/50757_normal.png?m=1392705722", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/75eb/5900/50757_large.png?m=1392705722", "created": 1385543365, "last_modified": 1392705722}, "last_reply_by": "Eagleyes", "last_touched": 1698458429, "title": "难道就这样过完一生吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/986042", "created": 1698391277, "deleted": 0, "content": "楼主老家湖北四线小县城的，大学毕业后去到一线城市， 见过 6-7 年的拼搏，在城市里买了房子，也背上了一个月快 1 万的房贷。\r\n买房第二年后，职业生涯开始走下坡路。最近刚刚失业了。\r\n\r\n在走下坡路的这 6 年里面，我无数次期望自己能重现雄起，但是失败了。期间有一段时间得了抑郁，不过现在人算好了，活过来。 \r\n\r\n现在又失业了。有时夜里醒来，问自己，难道就这样过完一生吗？ 有点不甘心，但是又对自己不够狠，人不够睿智，不是那么会来事。 \r\n\r\n每个人都会均值回归，大多数人终将平庸，而那个人为什么不能是我？对得起自己，对得起对你来讲重要的人", "content_rendered": "<p>楼主老家湖北四线小县城的，大学毕业后去到一线城市， 见过 6-7 年的拼搏，在城市里买了房子，也背上了一个月快 1 万的房贷。\n买房第二年后，职业生涯开始走下坡路。最近刚刚失业了。</p>\n<p>在走下坡路的这 6 年里面，我无数次期望自己能重现雄起，但是失败了。期间有一段时间得了抑郁，不过现在人算好了，活过来。 </p>\n<p>现在又失业了。有时夜里醒来，问自己，难道就这样过完一生吗？ 有点不甘心，但是又对自己不够狠，人不够睿智，不是那么会来事。 </p>\n<p>每个人都会均值回归，大多数人终将平庸，而那个人为什么不能是我？对得起自己，对得起对你来讲重要的人</p>\n", "last_modified": 1698391277, "replies": 68, "id": 986042}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d1fe/173d/79_large.png?m=1611762998", "name": "server", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d1fe/173d/79_normal.png?m=1611762998", "title": "服务器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/server", "topics": 2028, "footer": "", "header": "关于服务器选择和使用的技术讨论。", "title_alternative": "Server", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d1fe/173d/79_mini.png?m=1611762998", "stars": 2247, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 79, "parent_node_name": "webmaster"}, "member": {"id": 635392, "username": "dtekol", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dtekol", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b2317d0407f051712dd7bb18bf02561d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b2317d0407f051712dd7bb18bf0